title: George Zahringer
text:
George Zahringer III (born April 23, 1953 in <a href="Saginaw%2C%20Michigan">Saginaw, Michigan</a>) is an <a href="amateur">amateur</a> <a href="golf">golf</a>er and <a href="stockbroker">stockbroker</a> from <a href="New%20York%2C%20New%20York">New York, New York</a>. He attended <a href="Stonehill%20College">Stonehill College</a>.
